        <strong class="font-weight-bold">Tournament Results!</strong><br />
        <a href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#tournamentStatTimesModal" class="font-weight-bold text-primary">Start Times</a><br />
        Note - Entries are still being accepted for the Women’s Singles, ‘B’ Singles, ‘B’ and ‘C’ Womens’ Doubles and ‘C’ Mixed Doubles.<br />
